<DATE>01/17/2009</DATE>
<AUTHOR>Jack</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>Bought the 6.0ltr WT version two weeks before leaving Maryland. Installed cruise control and hauled 5500 lbs on a 16ft tandem trailer and 1000 lbs in the bed. Averaged 16mpg on Hwy after tuning with the Diablo Predator using 87 octane gas. I have the 4:10 HD posi-lock rear. I average 12-13 mph in town. I would have liked the 6spd Allison transmission.</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>Firm ride, drives and pulls great with the loads I've used so far.</FAVORITE>
